For outlining text in black for webpage

<style type="text/css">
.OutlineText {
	font: Tahoma, Geneva, sans-serif;
	font-size: 64px;
    color: white;
    text-shadow:
    /* Outline */
    -1px -1px 0 #000000,
    1px -1px 0 #000000,
    -1px 1px 0 #000000,
    1px 1px 0 #000000,  
    -2px 0 0 #000000,
    2px 0 0 #000000,
    0 2px 0 #000000,
    0 -2px 0 #000000; /* Terminate with a semi-colon */
}
</style>
